        "message": "=<html><body><h2>Manual SOW Send Required</h2><p>The SOW for <strong>{{ $('Collect Subfolder IDs').first().json.coacheeName }}</strong> ({{ $('Collect Subfolder IDs').first().json.clientCompany }}) is ready but no client email address was found in the transcript.</p><p><a href='{{ $('Collect Subfolder IDs').first().json.sowDocUrl }}'>View SOW</a></p><p>Please send manually to the client.</p></body></html>",
